## Ubuntu 

### Installation
1) install docker: https://docs.docker.com/engine/installation/linux/ubuntulinux/
2) install docker-compose: https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/

### Getting started
1- setting up the docker image
  1) docker build -t demo .
  2) verification step: docker run -it -p 3000:3000 -v $PWD:/app demo bash -l
2- setting up the docker-compose service & container
  1) docker-compose build
  2) docker-compose up -d db 
  3) docker-compose run app bash -l -c "rake db:create"
  4) docker-compose run app bash -l -c "rake db:migrate"
  5) docker-compose run app bash -l -c "rake db:seed"
  6) docker-compose up

### Starting the server
docker-compose run -p 3000:3000 app

### Debug
docker-compose run app bash -l

### cleaning docker-compose
docker-compose rm -f
docker-compose pull
docker-compose up --build -d